OL,3,CChildren's charity rejects Christmas
OL,4,Cdonation from Archbishop Justin Welby
OL,6,FA children's charity said it has
OL,7,Frejected the Archbishop of
OL,8,FCanterbury's Christmas donation as it
OL,9,Fwould "not be consistent" with its
OL,10,Fwork supporting victims of sexual
OL,11,Fabuse.
OL,13,FIn his annual Christmas e-card sent
OL,14,Fearlier this week, Justin Welby, who
OL,15,Fquit over his failure in handling a
OL,16,Fsex abuse case in the Church of
OL,17,FEngland, said he would be making a
OL,18,Fdonation to The Children's Society.
