OL,3,CChildren's charity rejects Christmas
OL,4,Cdonation from Archbishop Justin Welby
OL,6,FA message in the card noted that the
OL,7,Fcharity "works with children affected
OL,8,Fby criminal and sexual exploitation,
OL,9,Fabuse" and other issues.
OL,11,FHowever, on Friday the charity said it
OL,12,Fhas "respectfully decided" not to
OL,13,Faccept the donation after a review
OL,14,Ffound the Archbishop had failed to
OL,15,Freport allegations of abuse to the
OL,16,Fpolice.
