OL,3,CChildren's charity rejects Christmas
OL,4,Cdonation from Archbishop Justin Welby
OL,6,FChief executive of the charity, Mark
OL,7,FRussell, said: "After careful
OL,8,Fconsideration, we have respectfully
OL,9,Fdecided not to accept the donation
OL,10,Foffered by the outgoing Archbishop of
OL,11,FCanterbury.
OL,13,F"The Children's Society is deeply
OL,14,Fcommitted to supporting the survivors
OL,15,Fof abuse, our teams support victims of
OL,16,Fchild sexual abuse, and this means
OL,17,Fthat accepting this donation would not
OL,18,Fbe consistent with the principles and
OL,19,Fvalues that underpin our work."
