OL,3,CChildren's charity rejects Christmas
OL,4,Cdonation from Archbishop Justin Welby
OL,6,FAfter days of public pressure, Mr
OL,7,FWelby announced his resignation from
OL,8,Fthe Church "in sorrow with all victims
OL,9,Fand survivors of abuse" in the wake of
OL,10,Fthe Makin Review. He will officially
OL,11,Fstep down in January.
OL,13,FThe independent review found he had
OL,14,Ffailed to report serial abuser, John
OL,15,FSmyth to the police when he was made
OL,16,Faware of the allegations in 2013 and
OL,17,Fcould've brought Smyth to justice.
