OL,6,FBarrister John Smyth abused as many as
OL,7,F130 boys and men in the UK and Africa
OL,8,Fover five decades and is said to have
OL,9,Fsubjected his victims to traumatic
OL,10,Fphysical, sexual and psychological
OL,11,Fabuse.
OL,13,FSmyth died aged 77 in Cape Town, South
OL,14,FAfrica in 2018 while under
OL,15,Finvestigation by Hampshire Police and
OL,16,Fwas "never brought to justice for the
OL,17,Fabuse", the Makin report said.
