OL,6,FMr Russell added: "We were profoundly
OL,7,Fshocked by the findings of the Makin
OL,8,Freport, and our thoughts are with all
OL,9,Fsurvivors of abuse.
OL,11,F"We believe that there is an urgent
OL,12,Fneed for the Church of England to
OL,13,Freset its approach to safeguarding and
OL,14,Fcontinue to create a safer Church and
OL,15,Fsafer spaces for young people,
OL,16,Fprotected by real accountability and a
OL,17,Fculture of care.
